data.description: Fabulous 2-story townhome on a desirable location with light & bright and open floor plan. Turn key and ready to move in. This great home boasts a large living room with nice crown molding and space for dining area, remodeled kitchen with stainless steel appliances, and breakfast nook which leads out to the private and cozy patio. Spacious master bedroom with walk in closet, nicely remodeled bathroom, ceiling fans, and beautifully upgraded wood like & tile flooring. It also offers 2-car detached garage only steps away from the house. Enjoy the smart home features this home has to offer and community playground and convenient location of schools and shopping. Excellent starter home or investment property. Don't Miss Out on this Beauty!
